HPI 999 Fujitsubo Subaru Impreza (Dark Silver)

“Street” version of the Fujitsubo Impreza from the 2006 Super Taikyu Series seen here. Fujitsubo was established in 1931 and is a manufacturer of manifold and exhaust parts.
